{"id": 2620, "genre": 1001, "title": "双十一本来没怎么想花钱的你都是怎么破功的？", "description": "“哇，100元的券，不用不就亏了么！”结果凑了700多块钱的单。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Images ）", "record_count": 2020, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181112175607PbYNC6jS8L4w1moR.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 310528, "content": "京东买书，500-300，实在忍不住了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400633}, {"id": 310530, "content": "想想总要买的  加上朋友种草的 就破功了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497107}, {"id": 310531, "content": "零食满199减129（还有5元抵用金），很划算。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294659}, {"id": 310532, "content": "因为有红包，虽然额度不大，但感觉不用就是自己亏了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460104}, {"id": 312836, "content": "书店店员说他们双11有活动，所以我回来天猫上看了下，就剁手了(*^▽^)/★*☆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512099}, {"id": 310533, "content": "喜欢的博主仙女奔推推推，自然就买买买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493801}, {"id": 310535, "content": "淘宝的算法推送", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463428}, {"id": 312583, "content": "家里确实没纸/洗衣液/沐浴露/湿巾/猫粮了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1109939}, {"id": 310280, "content": "为了用 40 元的购物津贴，买了 500 多的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 234, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 310792, "content": "人到中年追求时髦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500664}, {"id": 310281, "content": "被好友发来的链接安利，就顺便一起团购买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 310538, "content": "愣是没用掉130元的购物津贴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464046}, {"id": 310540, "content": "加了5件购物车，结果一晚上过去，50个包裹", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469135}, {"id": 310541, "content": "错过了这次 以后再买就没有写完的优惠了……", "image": "img/option/option/20181113155151qRUNMzuZVOFa9AKe", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410193}, {"id": 310286, "content": "随便点开看看，结果抽中了红包，感觉不用就可惜了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 310543, "content": "400-50\n200-20", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501528}, {"id": 310544, "content": "就花了两元，其他的全部能量搞定，为什么不剁手？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474003}, {"id": 310800, "content": "看到299的零食大礼包的东西不错，而且还有抽锦鲤活动。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470215}, {"id": 310546, "content": "这些东西迟早都是要买的，现在买真的便宜很多欸～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500738}, {"id": 310547, "content": "400减50，拼命拉赞得来的红包不能浪费，浪费时间参加活动的红包不能浪费，so...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489170}, {"id": 310548, "content": "优惠随缘，只要把攒了两个月的购物车清空", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360999}, {"id": 310549, "content": "觉得不买可惜，错过还得等双十二", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181750}, {"id": 310550, "content": "确实便宜我才买的，付钱之前反复斟酌是否是我真正需要的东西，不为凑单而凑合", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501560}, {"id": 310552, "content": "错过了自己辛苦拉来的红包感觉会错过全世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471420}, {"id": 310553, "content": "给女生买零食🌚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501563}, {"id": 310555, "content": "满6000减600，比平常确实便宜不少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501583}, {"id": 310556, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501586}, {"id": 310558, "content": "店铺买6件打7折，然后12号0晨还没发货就退了5件，羊毛必须薅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501591}, {"id": 310559, "content": "什么都没买…感觉双十一买的东西都不怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831413}, {"id": 310561, "content": "正好需要的东西又比平时便宜就买了点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437787}, {"id": 310562, "content": "本来就想买鞋，整个双十一就买了一双鞋，便宜了不少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501603}, {"id": 310563, "content": "为了凑优惠券的使用门槛，买了一堆想要但是不买也没什么的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986384}, {"id": 310565, "content": "没事儿刷微淘。哇，这个又便宜（一点一点）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497692}, {"id": 310566, "content": "被淘宝天猫今年的双十一合伙人游戏带起来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982027}, {"id": 310568, "content": "现在不买以后也要买不如趁着双十一能优惠个十几二十块钱买买买吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468573}, {"id": 310569, "content": "从999降到799的鞋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449423}, {"id": 310570, "content": "为什么会有满400减50", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467614}, {"id": 310571, "content": "无意中发现天猫国际有款面膜半价……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049506}, {"id": 310572, "content": "所有满199减100的促销，本质原价都比原来贵的多的多，结果购物车早都超过200了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499146}, {"id": 310828, "content": "集了能量，不用可惜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1503000}, {"id": 310573, "content": "优衣库太便宜了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461806}, {"id": 310574, "content": "无数朋友问我买了什么。什么都没买的我就想着去看看吧。看着看着就买了一堆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432422}, {"id": 310575, "content": "这个99的鼠标降了三十块！我还有三十的红包！顺便再买个鼠标垫买双拖鞋买个读卡器买罐糖买支圆规.......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950214}, {"id": 310576, "content": "买马云的东西 还马云的钱😅", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500354}, {"id": 310577, "content": "我只是想买件毛衣碰巧双十一了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057745}, {"id": 310578, "content": "类似两件八折四件七折。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501664}, {"id": 310579, "content": "想买的书优惠了60块的时候，我毫不犹豫加入了购物大军。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501665}, {"id": 310580, "content": "钱又不是真正花出去了了，只是换种方式换个形态存在着", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1501650}, {"id": 311092, "content": "买了一台手机，其实可买可不买，不过也不后悔，因为新手机确实比原来的好用！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499458}, {"id": 310581, "content": "保证年内最低价，为什么不下手。囤货到明年618", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830523}]}